{"translation":{"id":"zh_web","name":"和合本","shortName":"CUV","englishName":"Chinese Union Version","language":"zho","languageName":"繁體/简体中文"},"book":{"id":"PSA","translationId":"zh_web","name":"诗篇","commonName":"诗篇","title":"诗篇","order":19,"numberOfChapters":150},"chapter":{"number":120,"content":[{"type":"verse","number":1,"content":["我在急难中呼求耶和华， 祂就应允我。"]},{"type":"verse","number":2,"content":["耶和华啊，求你救我的性命脱离说谎的嘴唇， 脱离诡诈的舌头。"]},{"type":"verse","number":3,"content":["诡诈的舌头啊，要给你什么？ 还要怎样待你呢？"]},{"type":"verse","number":4,"content":["就是勇士的利箭， 和杜松木的炭火。"]},{"type":"verse","number":5,"content":["我有祸了，因为我寄居在米设， 住在基达的帐棚中！"]},{"type":"verse","number":6,"content":["我的灵魂与恨恶和平的人 同住太久了。"]},{"type":"verse","number":7,"content":["我主张和平； 但我一开口，他们就主张战争。"]}]},"numberOfVerses":7}